claim.claim-text:
1. A communications device comprising:
first and second input terminals configured to provide coupling with respective first and second conductors of a communications line;
first and second signal conductors respectively coupled with the first and second input terminals;
a communications circuit coupled to the first and second signal conductors wherein the communications circuit provides a communications interface;
a test switch configured to electrically couple the first and second signal conductors responsive to activation thereof; and
an indicator circuit configured to provide indication of a completed electrical circuit through the test switch wherein the indicator circuit comprises a battery and at least one light emitting diode electrically coupled in series with the test switch and the communications circuit.
